	<body ng-app="sharikiLandingApp">
		<div ng-controller="LandingCtrl">
			<!-- Content -->
			<div class="container-fluid first-container landing">
				<div>
					<div class="row mtl">
						<div class="col-xs-8 col-xs-offset-2 col-md-offset-5 col-md-2">
							<img class="img-responsive img-logo" src="images/icons/svg/logo.svg">
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-offset-1 col-md-10 text-center">
							<h1 class="white-text">smart hotel booking</h1>
							<h4 class="grey-text">for smart travelers</h4>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-offset-4 col-md-2 text-center white-text mtl">	
							<a du-smooth-scroll duration="700" href="#info-container" class="btn btn-info btn-lg btn-block">learn more</a>
						</div>
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-2 text-center white-text mtl mbl">	
							<a du-smooth-scroll duration="700" href="#signup-container" class="btn btn-success btn-lg btn-block">launching soon</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="container-fluid info-container" id="info-container">
				<div class="container hidden-xs hidden-sm">
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-10 text-center">
							<h3>Booking a hotel should be easy, transparent and fun</h3>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="row top-margin">
						<div class="col-md-4 text-center">
							<i class="fa fa-heart fa-5x"></i>
							<h4>Honest Hotel Prices</h4>
							<p><small>Forget crossed out prices presented as "deals". We love transparency and if the hotel is overpriced - we will wholeheartedly tell you so. Likewise, if the hotel has a fantastic offer - we'll make sure you never miss it. We also give each hotel a value score, so you always know what you pay for.</small></p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-4 text-center">
							<i class="fa fa-eye fa-5x"></i>
							<h4>Intuitive Guidance</h4>
							<p><small>We store large amount of pricing data and we know which city, neighbourhood, hotel or room are the cheapest and when. And - we are willing to share. Flexible on your travel dates? Look for green dates on our calendar. Think which area of the city to stay in? Just follow the colors on the map.</small></p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-4 text-center">
							<i class="fa fa-bolt fa-5x"></i>
							<h4>Lightning Fast Experience</h4>
							<p><small>Enough is enough. No confusing marketing tricks here. Enjoy clean and beautiful  environment and feel like you are flying when using our fastest ever travel website. We say, one second spent on waiting is one second too much.</small></p>
						</div>
					</div>					
				</div>
				<div class="hidden-md hidden-lg">
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 text-center">
							<h3>Booking a hotel should be easy, transparent and fun</h3>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="row top-margin">
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 text-center">
							<i class="fa fa-heart fa-5x"></i>
							<h4>Honest Hotel Prices</h4>
							<p><small>Forget crossed out prices presented as "deals". We love transparency and if the hotel is overpriced - we will wholeheartedly tell you so. Likewise, if the hotel has a fantastic offer - we'll make sure you never miss it. We also give each hotel a value score, so you always know what you pay for.</small></p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 text-center">
							<i class="fa fa-eye fa-5x"></i>
							<h4>Intuitive Guidance</h4>
							<p><small>We store large amount of pricing data and we know which city, neighbourhood, hotel or room are the cheapest and when. And - we are willing to share. Flexible on your travel dates? Look for green dates on our calendar. Think which area of the city to stay in? Just follow the colors on the map.</small></p>
						</div>
