							<i class="fa fa-bolt fa-5x"></i>
							<h4>Lightning Fast Experience</h4>
							<p><small>Enough is enough. No confusing marketing tricks here. Enjoy clean and beautiful  environment and feel like you are flying when using our fastest ever travel website. We say, one second spent on waiting is one second too much.</small></p>
						</div>
					</div>					
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="container-fluid calendar-container">
				<div class="hidden-md hidden-lg">
					<div class="row mtl">
						<div class="col-xs-12 text-center">
							<div class="well well-sm well-opacity well-hulabuk">
								<h4>Sneak a Peek: when is it cheaper to visit Paris?</h4>	
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="col-xs-12 text-center">			
							<div class="well well-sm well-opacity well-hulabuk">
								<date-range-picker ng-model="selectedRange" always-visible="true" ranged="true" past-dates="true" calendar-averages="calendarAverages" class="row calendar-row ng-cloak"></date-range-picker>
								<div class="row">
									<div class="col-xs-2 col-md-2">
										<p class="pull-right">£</p>
									</div>
									<div class="col-xs-8 col-md-8">
										<div class="progress">
								            <div class="progress-bar nephritis" style="width: 12.5%;"></div>
								            <div class="progress-bar emerald" style="width: 12.5%;"></div>
								            <div class="progress-bar sunflower" style="width: 12.5%;"></div>
								            <div class="progress-bar orange" style="width: 12.5%;"></div>
