	          						</div>
		          						<div class="col-xs-2 col-md-2">
											<p>£££</p>
										</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="container-fluid signup-container" id="signup-container">
				<div>
					<div ng-show="!showUserFeedback" class="row">
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12" ng-cloak>
							<h3 class="white-text  text-center">Get notified when we go live!</h3>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div ng-show="showUserFeedback && emailValid" class="row mtl">
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-offset-4 col-md-4" >
							<div class="alert alert-success well-hulabuk text-center">Champion! We'll let you know once we are on.</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div ng-show="showUserFeedback && !emailValid" class="row mtl">
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-offset-4 col-md-4" ng-cloak>
							<div class="alert alert-warning well-hulabuk text-center">Hey, this doesn't look like a valid email!</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12 text-center">
							<h5 class="grey-text">No spam - we'll only send you an email once we launch.</h5>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-offset-3 col-md-4 mtl">
							<input type="text" class="form-control login-field" ng-model="email" placeholder="Enter your email address...">
						</div>
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-2 mtl">
							<a class="btn btn-block btn-lg btn-success" ng-click="signUp()">Get notified</a>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="row mtl ptl">
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12 text-center">
							<h6 class="grey-text">Get in touch:</h6>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="row mbl">
						<div class="col-xs-6 col-md-offset-5 col-md-1 text-center">
							<a href="mailto:team@hulabuk.com" class="text-muted"><i class="fa fa-envelope fa-3x"></i></a>
						</div>
						<div class="col-xs-6 col-md-1 text-center">
							<a href="https://twitter.com/hulabuk" class="text-muted"><i class="fa fa-twitter fa-3x"></i></a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
